data.description: Welcome to 2323 Walnut Bottom Road, Carlisle, PA 17015! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom traditional home with its inviting wrap-around porch is a true gem. Situated on a slight hill, this home offers breathtaking mountain views from the front and picturesque farm views from the back, providing you with the best of both worlds. One of the standout features of this property is the brand-new flooring that graces every corner of its spacious 2240 square feet. In addition to this, a fantastic 18x32' room was added in 2012, offering incredible versatility. Whether you envision it as an in-law suite, game room, playroom, or even a theater room, this space has endless possibilities. The convenience of a full bathroom on both the first and second levels adds to the practicality of this home. You'll also find a first-floor laundry room, making chores a breeze. The interior boasts beautiful hardwood trim throughout, adding a touch of elegance to the living spaces. And don't forget that all the appliances, which are less than 5 years old, will convey with the home. If you're in need of even more space, the finished basement area provides extra living or entertainment room, and there's plenty of storage available as well. Updates to the property include new garage doors, a high-efficiency propane furnace that was replaced just 2.5 years ago, and a water heater that is only 6 years old. The internal well components are also new, and the property features a UV filtration system, whole-home filter, and a water softener. The seller notes that the well depth is approximately 175 feet, and the well and septic are located at least 100 feet apart. The well is situated at the back, while the septic system is at the front of the property, approximately 5-10' from the bird bath, with the drain field close to the road. Outdoor living is equally inviting with an above-ground 24' pool complete with a freshly painted deck. And for those who love to entertain, the 16x30 Trex deck out back is perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The roof, a critical component of any home, is in great shape with the roof over the addition being redone in 2014. In summary, 2323 Walnut Bottom Road is not just a house; it's a wonderful place to call home. With its ample space, stunning views, and numerous upgrades, this property offers both comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
